## Links

* [Resque](https://github.com/resque/resque) – a Redis-backed library for running background jobs
* [Delayed Job](https://github.com/collectiveidea/delayed_job) – encapsulates the common pattern of asynchronously executing longer tasks in the background
* [Queue Classic](https://github.com/ryandotsmith/queue_classic) – a simple interface to a PostgreSQL-backed message queue
* [Sidekiq](http://sidekiq.org/) – simple, efficient background processing for Ruby